{
  "text": "Trials utilizing other SERMs chemoprevention are ongoing [CITATION_1] . These include the Raloxifene for Use in the Heart (RUTH) study [CITATION_2] in which breast cancer risk is assessed and the HOT study, in which low-dose tamoxifen added to HRT seeks to guage risk reduction [CITATION_3] . ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "43015407",
